125 grams Blueberries
2 sachet(s) Honey
½ sachet(s) Ground Cinnamon
220 grams Yoghurt
120 grams Granola
1 unit(s) Apple

Quarter, core and thinly slice the apple (peeling optional).
Share the yoghurt between two serving bowls.

Top the yoghurt with the blueberries and apple slices.

Scatter the granola over the fruit.
Drizzle over the honey and half the cinnamon to finish.